              "raw": "{{base_url}}/graphql",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["graphql"]
            },
            "description": "GraphQL **introspection** query — a capability unique to GraphQL. Clients can discover the entire schema without external documentation. There is no REST or RPC equivalent built into the protocol."
          },
